---
title: Falafels & Roast Veggie Couscous with Creamy Pesto Dressing & Roasted Almonds
description: When a wholesome dinner tastes as good as this one, it makes for a splendid night of tucking in. Let the sweet roasted veggies, couscous, crisp falafel and herby pesto dressing take you to a state of bliss.
